metadata.name: BattleSlayers #hidden
metadata.description: Battle slayers are a new class of warriors forged by combining new school tech with the heart of a traditional warrior.Owning a Battle Slayers will give you many benefits such as access to an exclusive group that will provide its holders pre-sale access to future collections, a private discord, best Alpha callers, project analysis, most sought after whitelist opportunities and weekly mystery box giveaways for holders.
